		<p>
			The falafel I used were pre-made and store-bought.
			However, you can make your own using this 
		       <a
			       href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/B003OBB8LC/?tag=lich048-20"
			       class="amazon">Gluten Free Falafel Mix</a> from Amazon.

		       Even better: make your own falafel from scratch using this
			<a class="bodybuilding"
				href="http://bodybuilding.7eer.net/c/102597/76781/2023?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bodybuilding.com%2Ffun%2Fask-the-protein-powder-chef-protein-falafel.html">Protein Falafel recipe</a> by Anna Sward, author and and
			founder of <a
				href="http://proteinpow.com/">Proteinpow</a>.
		She used pea protein powder in her falafel recipe. 	
		</p>
